    "shlok": [
      "Arjuna Uvaacha:\nSannyaasam karmanaam krishna punar yogam cha shamsasi;\nYacchreya etayorekam tanme broohi sunishchitam.",
      "Sri Bhagavaan Uvaacha:\nSannyaasah karmayogashcha nihshreyasakaraa vubhau;\nTayostu karmasannyaasaat karmayogo vishishyate.",
      "Jneyah sa nityasannyaasi yo na dweshti na kaangkshati;\nNirdwandwo hi mahaabaaho sukham bandhaat pramuchyate.",
      "Saankhyayogau prithagbaalaah pravadanti na panditaah;\nEkam apyaasthitah samyag ubhayor vindate phalam.",
      "Yatsaankhyaih praapyate sthaanam tad yogair api gamyate;\nEkam saankhyam cha yogam cha yah pashyati sa pashyati.",
      "Sannyaasastu mahaabaaho duhkham aaptuma yogatah;\nYogayukto munir brahma na chirenaadhigacchati.",
      "Yogayukto vishuddhaatmaa vijitaatmaa jitendriyah;\nSarvabhootaatmabhootaatmaa kurvannapi na lipyate.",
      "Naiva kinchit karomeeti yukto manyeta tattwavit;\nPashyan shrunvan sprishan jighran nashnan gacchan swapan shwasan.",
      "Pralapan visrijan grihnan nunmishan nimishannapi;\nIndriyaaneendriyaartheshu vartanta iti dhaarayan.",
      "Brahmanyaadhaaya karmaani sangam tyaktwaa karoti yah;\nLipyate na sa paapena padmapatram ivaambhasaa.",
      "Kaayena manasaa buddhyaa kevalair indriyair api;\nYoginah karma kurvanti sangam tyaktwaatmashuddhaye.",
      "Yuktah karmaphalam tyaktwaa shaantim aapnoti naishthikeem;\nAyuktah kaamakaarena phale sakto nibadhyate.",
      "Sarvakarmaani manasaa sannyasyaaste sukham vashee;\nNavadwaare pure dehee naiva kurvan na kaarayan.",
      "Na kartritwam na karmaani lokasya srijati prabhuh;\nNa karmaphala samyogam swabhaavas tu pravartate.",
      "Naadatte kasyachit paapam na chaiva sukritam vibhuh;\nAjnaanenaavritam jnaanam tena muhyanti jantavah.",
      "Jnaanena tu tad ajnaanam yeshaam naashitam aatmanah;\nTeshaam aadityavaj jnaanam prakaashayati tatparam.",
      "Tadbuddhayas tadaatmaanas tannishthaas tatparaayanaah;\nGacchantyapunaraavrittim jnaana nirdhoota kalmashaah.",
      "Vidyaavinaya sampanne braahmane gavi hastini;\nShuni chaiva shvapaake cha panditaah samadarshinah.",
      "Ihaiva tairjitah sargo yeshaam saamye sthitam manah;\nNirdosham hi samam brahma tasmaad brahmani te sthitaah.",
      "Na prahrishyet priyam praapya nodwijet praapya chaapriyam;\nSthirabuddhir asammoodho brahmavid brahmani sthitah.",
      "Baahyasparsheshwasaktaatmaa vindatyaatmani yat sukham;\nSa brahma yoga yuktaatmaa sukham akshayam ashnute.",
      "Ye hi samsparshajaa bhogaa duhkhayonaya eva te;\nAadyantavantah kaunteya na teshu ramate budhah.",
      "Shaknoteehaiva yah sodhum praak shareera vimokshanaat;\nKaamakrodhodbhavam vegam sa yuktah sa sukhee narah.",
      "Yo’ntah sukho’ntaraaraamas tathaantarjyotir eva yah;\nSa yogee brahma nirvaanam brahmabhooto’dhigacchati.",
      "Labhante brahma nirvaanam rishayah ksheenakalmashaah;\nCchinnadwaidhaa yataatmaanah sarvabhootahite rataah.",
      "Kaamakrodhaviyuktaanaam yateenaam yatachetasaam;\nAbhito brahma nirvaanam vartate viditaatmanaam.",
      "Sparsaan kritwaa bahir baahyaamschakshus chaivaantare bhruvoh;\nPraanaapaanau samau kritwaa naasaabhyantara chaarinau.",
      "Yatendriya manobuddhir munir mokshaparaayanah;\nVigatecchaabhaya krodho yah sadaa mukta eva sah.",
      "Bhoktaaram yajnatapasaam sarvaloka maheshwaram;\nSuhridam sarvabhootaanaam jnaatwaa maam shaantim ricchati.",
      "Hari Om Tat SatIti Srimad Bhagavadgeetaasoopanishatsu BrahmavidyaayaamYogashaastre Sri KrishnaarjunasamvaadeKarmasanyaasayogo Naama Panchamo’dhyaayah"
