      "Amee hi twaam surasanghaah vishantiKechid bheetaah praanjalayo grinanti;\nSwasteetyuktwaa maharshisiddhasanghaahStuvanti twaam stutibhih pushkalaabhih.",
      "Rudraadityaa vasavo ye cha saadhyaaVishwe’shvinau marutashchoshmapaashcha;\nGandharvayakshaasurasiddhasanghaaVeekshante twaam vismitaashchaiva sarve.",
      "Roopam mahat te bahuvaktranetramMahaabaaho bahubaahoorupaadam;\nBahoodaram bahudamshtraakaraalamDrishtwaa lokaah pravyathitaastathaa’ham.",
