      "Damshtraakaraalaani cha te mukhaaniDrishtwaiva kaalaanalasannibhaani;\nDisho na jaane na labhe cha sharmaPraseeda devesha jagannivaasa.",
      "Amee cha twaam dhritaraashtrasya putraahSarve sahaivaavanipaalasanghaih;\nBheeshmo dronah sootaputrastathaa’sauSahaasmadeeyairapi yodhamukhyaih.",
      "Vaktraani te twaramaanaa vishantiDamshtraakaraalaani bhayaanakaani;\nKechidwilagnaa dashanaantareshuSandrishyante choornitairuttamaangaih.",
      "Yathaa nadeenaam bahavo’mbuvegaahSamudramevaabhimukhaah dravanti;\nTathaa tavaamee naralokaveeraahVishanti vaktraanyabhivijwalanti.",
