      "Tejah kshamaa dhritih shauchamadroho naatimaanitaa;\nBhavanti sampadam daiveem abhijaatasya bhaarata.",
      "Dambho darpo’bhimaanashcha krodhah paarushyameva cha;\nAjnaanam chaabhijaatasya paartha sampadamaasureem.",
      "Daivee sampadvimokshaaya nibandhaayaasuree mataa;\nMaa shuchah sampadam daiveem abhijaato’si paandava.",
      "Dwau bhootasargau loke’smin daiva aasura eva cha;\nDaivo vistarashah proktah aasuram paartha me shrinu.",
