      "Chintaamaparimeyaam cha pralayaantaamupaashritaah;\nKaamopabhogaparamaa etaavaditi nishchitaah.",
      "Aashaapaashashatairbaddhaah kaamakrodhaparaayanaah;\nEehante kaamabhogaartha manyaayenaarthasanchayaan.",
      "Idamadya mayaa labdham imam praapsye manoratham;\nIdamasteedamapi me bhavishyati punardhanam.",
      "Asau mayaa hatah shatrur hanishye chaaparaanapi;\nEeshwaro’hamaham bhogee siddho’ham balavaan sukhee.",
      "Aadhyo’bhijanavaanasmi ko’nyosti sadrisho mayaa;\nYakshye daasyaami modishye ityajnaanavimohitaah.",
