      "Adeshakaale yaddaanamapaatrebhyashcha deeyate;\nAsatkritamavajnaatam tattaamasamudaahritam.",
      "Om tatsaditi nirdesho brahmanas trividhah smritah;\nBraahmanaastena vedaashcha yajnaashcha vihitaah puraa.",
      "Tasmaadomityudaahritya yajnadaanatapahkriyaah;\nPravartante vidhaanoktaah satatam brahmavaadinaam.",
