      "Hari Om Tat SatIti Srimad Bhagavadgeetaasoopanishatsu BrahmavidyaayaamYogashaastre Sri KrishnaarjunasamvaadeShraddhaatrayavibhaagayogo Naama Saptadasho’dhyaayah"
